===Head Instructor===
{{flavour|A powerful warrior-mage who instructs aspiring students in physical, magical, and anti-magical combat.}}
[[File:Head Instructor.png]] The '''Head Instructor''' is a [[deep elf blademaster]] that dual-wields 2 [[antimagic]]-branded [[triple sword]]s. Its name will be randomized.

'''Spells'''
*[[Summon Mana Viper]]
*[[Dimension Anchor]]
*[[Blink Close]]
*[[Bolt of Devastation]] (3d20)

